  <string name="wifi_vendor_elements_help">Vendor-specific information elements ezithunyelwa ku-AP beacons kanye probe responses. Faka i-hex-encoded vendor IE body eyodwa nge-line, isibonelo &lt;tt&gt;AABBCC01&lt;/tt&gt;. Ungafaki &lt;tt&gt;0xDD&lt;/tt&gt; element ID noma length byte.</string>
